\r\n\r\n只有少数需要本地编译的程序员、需要绘图的艺术家等需要大内存，自己加钱配置就好了。", "content_rendered": "<p>很简单，国外没有微信、QQ 这种古怪的东西。在 macbook 上，工作联系一律用 email （自带的邮件客户端即可），亲朋好友聊天用手机就可以了，不会在电脑上聊天。</p>\n<p>大部分程序员都是远程连接 Linux 服务器进行开发，一般不会在 macbook 本地进行编译。</p>\n<p>所以大部分人在 macbook 本地运行的软件就是 safari 浏览器、邮件客户端、word 、excel 、ppt ，程序员外加一个 vscode ，用得着 8G 以上内存吗？</p>\n<p>只有少数需要本地编译的程序员、需要绘图的艺术家等需要大内存，自己加钱配置就好了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1709609268, "replies": 73, "id": 1020715}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 215903, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4115, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 650572, "username": "BlackSiao", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/BlackSiao", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2601b295629d00c16c1426d646626191?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2601b295629d00c16c1426d646626191?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2601b295629d00c16c1426d646626191?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1695614854, "last_modified": 1702004575}, "last_reply_by": "dyv9", "last_touched": 1709682173, "title": "大家平时用的都是什么邮箱捏？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1020706", "created": 1709608354, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，我现在大部分的邮箱验证还是用很早之前创建的 QQ 邮箱解决了，大家有没有更好的代替呢？", "content_rendered": "如题，我现在大部分的邮箱验证还是用很早之前创建的 QQ 邮箱解决了，大家有没有更好的代替呢？", "last_modified": 1709614627, "replies": 69, "id": 1020706}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cd